                                            ****First read me before use*****
          
          
It is a simple web crawler but gives result far better than a perfect web crawler.

Keep this into a directory(e.g. KanjiSpider)
Goto your terminal and type the following:
 
 1.mkdir KanjiSpider
 2.cd KanjiSpider
 3.goto crawl() method in KanjiSpider.py module and uncomment createDB() and comment line no.56(i.e. resetDB()) to line no.73(i.e. break)
 4.goto terminal and type python KanjiSpider.py
 5.again goto crawl() method in KanjiSpider.py module and comment createDB() and uncomment line no.56(i.e. resetDB()) to line no.73(i.e. break) 
 6.goto terminal and type python KanjiSpider.py
 7.you will be prompt for a url.enter it and watch what KanjiSpider can do!!!!
 
 
                                            ****Have Fun*****